==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paddlefish
<hw>Pad"dle*fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool)</fld>
<def>A large ganoid fish (<spn>Polyodon spathula</spn>) found in the
rivers of the Mississippi Valley. It has a long spatula-shaped snout.
Called also <altname>duck-billed cat</altname>, and <altname>spoonbill
sturgeon</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paddler</ent>⟦br⟧
